{
  "stem": "18575.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 500.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But then a committee send out-- send out-- spies, or whatever, there, from ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they confirmed it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That what they saw that the transports are going in and nothing coming out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And no people can be seen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That they killing there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they saw the crematoria, you know, the smoke from crematorium.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "The stink.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The stink is like you burn liver, or you burn meat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Sometimes you burn something in the stove, meat, there's a specific-- or nails that burns, or hair.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Burning hair gives you the same smell as cremation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they came back and they say, they're killing us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then people start hiding.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in February 1943-- there were several actions in between.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They took-- like 70% of the ghetto was emptied.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were two ghettos, actually, in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Was a large ghetto and a small ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were connected by a bridge over the so-called Aryan site.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were two separate islands.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Small ghetto and a street called [NON-ENGLISH], [POLISH] street in Polish, was separating them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So after the actions, they just closed up the small ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was only the large ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they made it smaller.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They-- they evacuated people, whoever was left and could show documents that it's working for German enterprise, into smaller portion of the large ghetto.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The remnants there started hiding.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People were buying documents, falsifying documents.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Germans were changing their-- their rules.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You could-- you are excluded only if you have documents, x type of document.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then those documents are not valid anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Only those documents are valid.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the natural reaction of people-- those that they had the right documents, I'm safe, you know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But organization-- a resistance organization start forming.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
